    "attributes": {
        "action": "Clarify the legal definition of \u201cadjacent to a highway\u201d in planning law",
        "additional_details": "We want the government to make a judgement on what counts as adjacent to a public highway or footway for permitted development rights and give a distance in metres. Otherwise, we think local authorities have too much authority.",
        "background": "There is no legal definition of what counts as \u201cadjacent\u201d to a public highway or footway. We think this creates confusion and inconsistent decisions by local authorities.",
